{"tid":1667114,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(公投) 最後會係畜生贏定係我地贏","createTime":"2019-10-21T09:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T10:01:54.000Z","uid":33789,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef3540ad391829be8cf1273954a205dada0ba921","tid":1667114,"uid":33789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"件事已經進入最後直路,先唔講大BOSS既港共中共,就3萬畜生而言,到底最後係解散畜生隊,定係香港人逐一被清算,就你自己既睇法投票<br />\n<br />\n正評: 解散畜生隊,重組光復警隊<br />\n負評: 香港人被逐一清算,之後做三等公民"},{"pid":"16c06f9fb93fc82e4f21d53af1d400f49ba36223","tid":1667114,"uid":33789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e3ab52228560e9fae588a217a9a4de40bb06e8","tid":1667114,"uid":33789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"我自己就唔係好樂觀,總係覺得香港人會被一少撮人搞到從此以後變成下等公民"},{"pid":"8443a061dad049bd141ff0323aa666efebb863a1","tid":1667114,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"唔想做失敗撚 但行動再唔升級就勝算不大"},{"pid":"e0ddebfbfaa4325b8607564e8653fffe25bae232","tid":1667114,"uid":33789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎投下一票"},{"pid":"9a5ca0e4fbd42c7adc90eb92021131296e77ce0b","tid":1667114,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"a96928acb484ed839d9054bb75070e3b60ab7e76","tid":1667114,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:51:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">想贏嘅同我入嚟<br />\n快啲把握最好時機</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n係時候搞個 尊重宗教自由大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bc92527348fa97c6efb0c52c3c08072ac692a397","tid":1667114,"uid":184370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"樓主開行動po好過啦<br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"ce281e2a8d5a907e5985c562b1d9edc883f777d6","tid":1667114,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:57:26.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"591a4a4536e60a5215be99ef359c281129159d25","tid":1667114,"uid":77551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"態度不正確 <br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"b32705a94b28132d199755bd552beafbaf81e6f0","tid":1667114,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"最後直路？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你地知唔知反共係一輩子既事</strong></span></span><br />\n好多人都識講革命，但唔知革命係乜<br />\n攬炒你估幾個月就完？太天真了"}]}